Senator Dino Melaye has alerted the public on police attempt to breaking into his house to forcefully arrest him. Melaye disclosed this early Wednesday morning via a tweet on his Twitter handle. He tweeted: “Police bringing in tool boxes to break doors and vandalize my house. Police EOD truck just brought them. Media take note.” Police bringing in tool boxes to break doors and vandalize my house. Police EOD truck just brought them. Media take note — Senator Dino Melaye (@dino_melaye) January 2, 2019 